<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="background-color: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},</span><br><br><span style="background-color: white;">As I’ve not heard back from any of my previous attempts to provide you with a quote for your business insurance, I will now be closing your records on our system.</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span><font face="arial">However, if you are&nbsp;<b>interested in proceeding with your quote</b>&nbsp;at any time in the future, please reply with the best date and time for me to call you. Alternatively, you can always give me a ring on&nbsp;<b>01242 808 740</b>.</font><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><font face="arial"><span style="background-color: white;">Kind regards,</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!User.FirstName}<br></font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><font face="Arial, sans-serif">E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></font></span><font style="font-size: 12pt;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
